column5: But, it isn't the first time we came home in the snow,  Give me a week of plus temps and it'll be Brownies in the skinny water
I can whip up a smitty that will pull that thing out on the ice hear. Just give the word.  Was on a solid 10" up here this morning.

yes by, well you're welcome to it!. I like my water the way she comes out of the tap. the big lake is only a week of warm temps and spring rain from some nice colour in the shallows. Best place for ice is in my cooler chillin the days catch  its in there somewhere

yes by, well you're welcome to it!.    Boy if I could of had one build over night, you would of enjoyed your time on the hard water. Sun was shining,no wind and it was +6 by 10 am.  Just sit back and enjoy the rays.
